msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/core/scheduler.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.core.scheduler.BaseScheduler.enqueue_request:5
msgid ""
"If ``False``, the engine will fire a ``request_dropped`` signal, and will "
"not make further attempts to schedule the request at a later time. For "
"reference, the default Scrapy scheduler returns ``False`` when the request "
"is rejected by the dupefilter."
msgstr ""

